            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-65fb807d23063af6-7a2b93 twpub-65fb807d23063af6-de533d twpub-65fb807d23063af6-6b4cd0\"><p class=\"foot\"><span class=\"c3\">108</span> (<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/65fb807d23063af6/text/000000031\">return</$link>)<br>\n[ L.â All the 4tos &quot;Lechery.&quot;âHere I have made the alteration recommended by Mr. Collier in his Preface to COLERIDGE'S SEVEN LECTURES ON SHAKESPEARE AND MILTON, p. cviii.]</p></div>"
        },
