            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-65fb807d23063af6-7a2b93 twpub-65fb807d23063af6-de533d twpub-65fb807d23063af6-6b4cd0\"><p>What follows, shews that the words which I have omitted ought to have no place in the text; nor is there any thing equivalent to them in the corresponding passage of the play as given in the later 4tos.]</p></div>"
        },
