            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/65fb807d23063af6/text/000000305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-65fb807d23063af6-7a2b93 twpub-65fb807d23063af6-de533d twpub-65fb807d23063af6-6b4cd0\"><p class=\"foot\"><span class=\"c3\">131</span> (<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/65fb807d23063af6/text/000000031\">return</$link>)<br>\n[ Enter EMPEROR, &amp;c.â SceneâAn apartment in the Emperor's Palace. According to THE HISTORY OF DR. FAUSTUS, the Emperor &quot;was personally, with the rest of the nobles and gentlemen, at the towne of Inzbrack, where he kept his court.&quot; Sig. G, ed. 1648.]</p></div>"
        },
